{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2014-10-31-challenge-of-interdisciplinary-learning","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"跨領域學習的挑戰","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"http://blog.fntsr.tw/articles/169/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Site is undergoing maintenance"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"十月結束了，開學已有三旬半月，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n第一次感受到自己對新生活上，調試得極度不適應。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"研究生生活。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"困境"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"困境"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"從歷史系跳到資工系軟工所，仍有一個很大的鴻溝，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n儘管我名義上已經踏入了，但是學識上仍浮載浮沈。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n或許，是我之前太過於樂觀，以為自己實作的經驗能替我克服，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n深刻體驗後，卻深深感受到許多沮喪與挫折。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在理論上，我是有太多不足需要補齊。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n尤其是數學面向，一向是我的罩門，此時更倍感艱辛，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n面對應用密碼學和各演算法，我感到被高牆籠罩的壓迫。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在報 Paper 這件事，也是重重打擊了自己，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n原本以為在時間內能完成，隨著時間逼近，越是慌亂。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n還好，可能是因為第一次報論文，才沒被盯到牆上。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n但是這種上台充滿著焦慮與沒信心的感受，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n卻也讓我感到丟臉與沮喪，和之前在PHPConf的感受大相徑庭。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這些日子以來，讓我缺乏時間管理的弱點，暴露得更明顯。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n做事喜歡隨心而起的個性，也讓我每件事都有做，卻都做不好。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n一直在事情沒做完與做不好的恐懼下度過。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我是知道會這樣的，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n只是真的在這些事發生時，才發現自己根本心理建設不夠。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"別日"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"別日"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我很懷念以前在歷史系時，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n偶爾讀讀歷史，然後自由時間都玩資訊的時光，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n儘管不用太認真上課，卻也能夠遊刃有餘的Pass每科考試。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n（儘管分數不高，但讀考試時卻也很開心）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"但我已經無法再用這種態度面對自己現在的生活了，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n其實這也是理所當然的。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我好想繼續鑽研自己喜歡的技術，去實作自己想做的作品，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n但是我現在讓自己走了這條路，這些事已經不能當作主要目標，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n心裡充滿了許多矛盾。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"有太多事情無法再用過去的生活方式去面對，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n我也沒有太多時間埋手在過去的時光，"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n而必須認真思考，思考我該怎麼做，怎麼改變。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"i